    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;tabs-wc&gt;</code> component transforms a group of <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> elements into a tab interface. Without JavaScript, it works as an accordion. With JavaScript, it adds keyboard navigation and ARIA tab semantics.</p>

